
units           metal
atom_style      atomic
boundary        p p p

read_data       zn_unitcell.data
Reading data file ...
  triclinic box = (0 0 0) to (2.66 2.3036276 4.93696) with tilt (-1.33 0 0)
WARNING: Triclinic box skew is large. LAMMPS will run inefficiently. (src/domain.cpp:220)
  1 by 1 by 1 MPI processor grid
  reading atoms ...
  2 atoms
  read_data CPU = 0.011 seconds

# Pair style and MEAM potential
pair_style      meam/c
pair_coeff      * * library.meam Zn Mg ZnMg.meam Zn

# Neighbor settings
neighbor        2.0 bin
neigh_modify    delay 10 check yes

# Thermo output
thermo          50
thermo_style    custom step pe etotal lx ly lz press pxx pyy pzz vol

# Optional trajectory dump
dump            1 all atom 100 dump.zn.lammps.trj

# Box relaxation (anisotropic for hcp Zn)
fix             1 all box/relax aniso 0.0 vmax 0.001

# Energy minimization - Box relaxation
min_style       cg
min_modify      line quadratic dmax 0.1
minimize        1e-12 1e-12 20000 20000
